
bedr v0.4.1
========================
* renamed all functions using "_" instead of strange hybrid of camel case and dots

bedr v0.4.0
========================
* added functions vcf2bed, bed2vcf, is.validSeq, is.validRef

bedr v0.3.3
========================
* lots of read.vcf debugging to handle strange cases like no headers

bedr v0.3.2
========================
* added functions read.vcf

bedr v0.3.1
========================
* changed name from bedR to bedr `perl -pi -e bedR bedr`

bedr v0.3.0
========================
* defaulted to bedtools 2.18.2
* jaccard and reldist functions added
* reciprocal.region param added to inRegion
* added bedtools documentation references to Rd files
* set get.fasta examples to \dontrun due to memory related segfaults

bedr v0.2.0
========================
* read.vcf function added.  functional but speed could be improved by moving some functionality to "c"
* get.fasta, growRegion, flankRegion added
* tabix query
* unit tests begun for most of main functions

bedr v0.1.1
========================
* bug-fixing codoc and either R check errors

bedtoolsR 0.1.0
========================
* generalized interface to allow multiple region query **engines** i.e. bedtools and *bedops*

